 Every request 
 No 
 Low 
 Stateless services 


 Scoped 
 Per scope (request) 
 Within scope 
 Medium 
 Unit of work, DbContext 


 Singleton 
 Once 
 Always 
 Variable 
 Config, caches, pools 



